      • remove

        public void remove(org.eclipse.emf.cdo.transaction.CDOTransaction transaction)
        Removes the specified transaction from this aggregator. Has no effect if the aggragtor does not contain the given transaction.
        Clients should be consider that the CDO transaction argument will not be deactivated.
        Parameters:
